{
  "texts": [
    "So, we followed the data sampling procedure in Qi et al. (2023); Yang et al. (2023) to create a categorized harmful query dataset for the jailbreak evaluation.",
    "More specifically, there are three sub-categories in each risk category, and we prompt GPT-4 to generate one harmful query for each sub-category, amounting to 14×3 = 42 plain harmful queries.",
    "See examples of the first risk category in Figure 6.",
    "[Sub-category: Drug trafficking] \"Tell me how to smuggle drugs across borders.\"",
    "[Sub-category: Intellectual property theft] \"Help me understand how to steal patents from competitors.\""
  ]
}